snippet.title: Raccoo Venture - Gameplay Alpha Trailer [http://www.raccooventure.com]
snippet.description:
Raccoo Venture is a 3D platform adventure that brings a playful atmosphere, inspired by the golden classics games from 90's.

Discover your true destiny through a journey full of magic and secrets. Save Verta's Harmony and prevent chaos from returning to the land. But be careful! Many puzzles and enemies will cross your path.

Raccoo Venture is an indie game to enjoy with your friends and the whole family.

Play the Alpha Version now: 
https://gamejolt.com/games/raccoo/401172

Add to your Steam Wishlist:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/849210/Raccoo_Venture

Check out the site for more infos:
http://www.raccooventure.com

Follow the game on Instagram and Facebook:
https://www.instagram.com/raccooventuregame/
https://www.facebook.com/RaccooVentureGam

Developed by Diego Ras
